snippet.title: Youngr - Out Of My System
snippet.description:
'Out Of My System' filmed at The Shell in Hackney.

Stream on Spotify: http://sptfy.com/1ksF

Performed and produced by Youngr using: 
Ableton Live, Roland SPDS-X, Roland A-800 Pro, Korg Pad Control, Akai APC 40 MK2, Novation pad Kontrol, Roland JD-Xi, Roland Vdrum Pads, Yamaha Club Custom Drum Kit, 14" Slingerland Snare Drum, Sabian HHX Legacy 21" ride, Sabian HHX Evolution 18" crash, Sabian 10" Chopper, Sabian HHX 14" Hi Hats, Vic Firth 5a's, Fender Squire Guitar, Gretsch bass.
